Description:
video: Add GST_VIDEO_FORMAT_NV12_128C8 for Broadcom SAND
 8bit format

Adds the new format GST_VIDEO_FORMAT_NV12_128C8 as a column-striped
NV12 used on the Raspberry Pi HEVC decoder.

 .
 gst-plugins-base1.0 (1.26.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium
 .
   * d/copyright: review with licenserecon
   * New upstream version 1.26.2
Author: Marc Leeman <marc.leeman@gmail.com>

